  "prompt": "Which is the best college for MBA in Delhi?",
  "response": "The best college for MBA in Delhi can depend on various factors such as faculty, placements, infrastructure, and student reviews. However, some of the top institutions frequently recognized for their MBA programs in Delhi include:\n\n1. **Faculty of Management Studies (FMS), University of Delhi**: FMS is consistently ranked as one of the top business schools in India, known for its excellent faculty, strong alumni network, and high placement records.\n\n2. **Indian Institute of Foreign Trade (IIFT)**: IIFT is renowned for its MBA program in International Business and has a strong reputation for placements and industry exposure.\n\n3. **International Management Institute (IMI)**: IMI offers a robust MBA curriculum and is well-regarded for its academic rigor and industry connections.\n\n4. **Management Development Institute (MDI), Gurgaon**: Although technically located in Gurgaon, MDI is often associated with Delhi and known for its high-quality MBA program and strong placement record.\n\n5. **Department of Management Studies (DMS), IIT Delhi**: DMS-IIT Delhi is another prestigious institution offering a full-time MBA with a reputation for rigorous academics and excellent placements.\n\nChoosing the best college would ultimately depend on your specific criteria and career goals. It's advisable to research each institution thoroughly and reach out to current students and alumni to better understand the pros and cons of each program.",
